%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor COE as CoE Head

participant UI as Schedule Approval UI
participant BFF as Project Planning BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant PPS as Project Planning Service
participant ADP as Service Adapter
participant DB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant KAFKA@{ "type": "queue", "alias": "Message Bus"}

COE->>UI: Open Schedule Approval
UI->>BFF: Load proposal
BFF->>ORCH: Get proposed schedule
ORCH->>PPS: Fetch proposal details
PPS->>DB: Query schedule_approval and planning data
DB-->>PPS: Proposal
PPS-->>ORCH: Proposal response
ORCH-->>BFF: Response
BFF-->>UI: Show review screen

alt Approve
    COE->>UI: Approve schedule
    UI->>BFF: Submit approval
    BFF->>ORCH: Start approval flow
    ORCH->>PPS: Approve schedule and freeze baseline
    PPS->>DB: Update schedule_approval = Approved
    PPS->>DB: Update project_planning status = Resource Tagging Pending
    PPS->>DB: Set baseline_frozen_flag = true
    ORCH->>ADP: Send notifications
    ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish ScheduleApproved Event
    ORCH-->>BFF: Success
    BFF-->>UI: Show approved state
else Send Back
    COE->>UI: Send back schedule
    UI->>BFF: Submit send back
    BFF->>ORCH: Start send back flow
    ORCH->>PPS: Update schedule status = Sent Back
    PPS->>DB: Update schedule_approval
    PPS->>DB: Insert status history
    ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish ScheduleSentBack Event
    ORCH-->>BFF: Success
    BFF-->>UI: Show sent back state
end
